        <Parent_String>British Renaissance-Baroque by reign [300112604], British Renaissance-Baroque styles [300021034], Renaissance-Baroque regional styles [300112572], Renaissance-Baroque styles [300021033], Renaissance-Baroque styles and periods [300021031], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
